    "rich_text_DyLi7P": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_y9aXFf": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Benefits for Skin & Mind",
            "heading_tag": "h3"
          }
        },
        "richtext_waV6LG": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Soaking in a warm bath should feel like a retreat for your skin and soul. Our bubble bombs and bars are crafted to nourish, relax, and uplift - naturally.</p><ul><li><strong>Deep Relaxation</strong> – The calming scents and fizzing bubbles melt away stress and promote mental clarity. A warm foaming bubble bath helps reset your mood after a long day.</li><li><strong>Soft, Hydrated Skin</strong> – Made with shea butter and oils, each bomb delivers intense moisture. Your skin feels silky smooth and refreshed after every use.</li><li><strong>Aromatherapy Boost</strong> – Infused with natural essential oils, our bombs enhance your bath with scent therapy. From calming lavender to energizing citrus, every bath supports your emotional wellness.</li><li><strong>Gentle for All Ages</strong> – Our formulas are kid-safe, non-toxic, and sensitive-skin friendly. Even our bubble bath liquid is free from synthetic dyes and sulfates.</li><li><strong>Fun & Colorful Experience</strong> – Watch your tub transform with swirls of color and sparkle. Bath time becomes a joyful, sensory escape.</li></ul>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_y9aXFf",
        "richtext_waV6LG"
      ],
