    "rich_text_9wVFaj": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_HqhWem": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "How to Use for Best Results",
            "heading_tag": "h3"
          }
        },
        "richtext_bpeCRB": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Turn your bath into a spa-like experience with just a few simple steps. Follow these tips to enjoy every fizzy, fragrant moment.</p><ul><li><strong>Start with Warm Water</strong> – Fill your tub with warm (not hot) water for optimal fizz and fragrance. This helps activate the ingredients and soothe your skin.</li><li><strong>Drop and Swirl</strong> – Add your bath bomb or bar once the tub is full. Let it fully dissolve and swirl the water to mix evenly.</li><li><strong>Soak for 15–20 Minutes</strong> – Relax in the tub while the oils and butters hydrate your skin. A calm soak helps absorb all the nourishing goodness.</li><li><strong>Use a Non Toxic Bubble Bath</strong> – Pair with our non toxic bubble bath for extra bubbles without irritation. It’s safe for kids, gentle on skin, and free of harmful chemicals.</li><li><strong>Rinse and Pat Dry</strong> – After soaking, rinse lightly and pat your skin dry. There’s no need to scrub - let the oils keep working post-bath.</li></ul>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_HqhWem",
